\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}\in\overline{\Omega}$
\end_inset

 tal que 
\begin_inset Formula $\max_{x\in\overline{\Omega}}u\left(x\right)=u\left(x_{0}\right)$
\end_inset

.
 Si 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}\in\partial\Omega$
\end_inset

