\begin_inset Formula $\max_{\overline{\Omega}}u\leq\max_{\overline{\Omega}}v_{\varepsilon}=\max_{\partial\Omega}v_{\varepsilon}\leq\max_{\partial\Omega}u+\varepsilon\max_{\partial\Omega}\left|x\right|^{2}$
\end_inset

