Ahora bien, 
\begin_inset Formula $E\left(g\right)\geq0$
\end_inset

, como 
\begin_inset Formula $g_{|\partial\Omega}=0$
\end_inset

, entonces 
\begin_inset Formula $\int_{\partial\Omega}\left(\nabla u\cdot\overrightarrow{n}\right)g=0$
\end_inset

, y 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta u=0$
\end_inset

