\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $u\left(t,x,y\right)=\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\sum_{m=1}^{\infty}\left[A_{n,m}\cos\left(c\rho_{n,m}t\right)+B_{n,m}\sin\left(c\rho_{n,m}t\right)\right]\sin\left(\frac{n\pi x}{L_{1}}\right)\sin\left(\frac{m\pi y}{L_{2}}\right)$
